docs.lead_paragraph: In the good ship Falcon, which has called away to carry a band of intrepid voyagers up into the frozen regions, was noticed as a part of its cargo a sewing machine. Mrs. Peary has told of the prize which a needle proved to the Esquimau woman, and how on her previous voyage, one of them unprovided with such a treasure came and asked for one of them, offering her child in exchange.
